<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #0f172a; color: #f8fafc; }
        .glass { background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="p-6 flex justify-between items-center glass sticky top-0 z-50">
        <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            ASTRODATAHUB
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-blue-400 transition">Back to Terminal</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        
        <section class="text-center mb-20">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">How can we assist your mission?</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">Our ground control team is standing by to help you navigate the platform.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            
            <section class="glass p-8 rounded-2xl">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-blue-500">●</span> Open a Support Ticket
                </h2>
                <form action="#" class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-300">Subject</label>
                        <select class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none">
                            <option>Technical Issue</option>
                            <option>Course Access Problem</option>
                            <option>Account Security</option>
                            <option>Feedback & Suggestions</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-300">Transmission Details</label>
                        <textarea rows="5" class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-3 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none text-slate-200" placeholder="Describe your issue..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold transition duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/20">
                        Send Transmission
                    </button>
                </form>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <details class="glass p-4 rounded-xl cursor-pointer group">
                        <summary class="font-semibold text-slate-200 group-hover:text-blue-400 list-none flex justify-between">
                            How do I track my progress?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">▾</span>
                        </summary>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">Head to your Dashboard. Each mission displays a real-time progress bar calculated based on completed modules.</p>
                    </details>

                    <details class="glass p-4 rounded-xl cursor-pointer group">
                        <summary class="font-semibold text-slate-200 group-hover:text-blue-400 list-none flex justify-between">
                            Can I access modules offline?
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">▾</span>
                        </summary>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">Currently, AstroDataHub requires an active satellite link (Internet connection) to synchronize your data.</p>
                    </details>

                    <details class="glass p-4 rounded-xl cursor-pointer group">
                        <summary class="font-semibold text-slate-200 group-hover:text-blue-400 list-none flex justify-between">
                            I found a bug in the code.
                            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">▾</span>
                        </summary>
                        <p class="mt-3 text-slate-400 text-sm">Please report all system anomalies via the contact form on the left. Our engineers will investigate.</p>
                    </details>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="relative flex h-3 w-3">
                        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75"></span>
                        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-emerald-500"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest">System Status</p>
                        <p class="text-emerald-200/70 text-xs">All systems operational. Satellite uptime: 99.9%</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>